ss=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 24, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104quj1665703548199.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/quj1665703548199.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/quj1665703548199.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"quj1665703548199\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">An element in a user interface that represents an entity, field, or operation call. It determines the appearance and behavior of the field, and the way the user enters or selects values in the field.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"quj1665703548199__p_d1730e1_d1731e1_d1732e1\">Do not use UDO widgets.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"quj1665703548199__p_d1733e1_d1734e1_d1735e1\">Determines the appearance and behavior of a field.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"quj1665703548199__p_d1736e1_d1737e1_d1738e1\">In character mode, a widget that is not supported is mapped to another widget type.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"quj1665703548199__p_d1739e1_d1740e1_d1741e1\">Click a widget to give the field focus. Do not use \"click on\".</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"quj1665703548199__p_d1742e1_d1743e1_d1744e1\">A field is painted on a component; the widget type is a property of the field. Each widget type has properties of its own.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"quj1665703548199__p_d1745e1_d1746e1_d1747e1\">A field has a value; a widget does not.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"quj1665703548199__p_d1748e1_d1749e1_d1750e1\">A physical widget can be \"standard\" or \"custom\". A physical widget can be mapped to one or more logical widgets in the initialization file. (The logical widget name appears in the Widget Type list on the Define Field form.)</p>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531430\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531430\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "widget Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 24, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 An element in a user interface that represents an entity, field, or operation call. It determines the appearance and behavior of the field, and the way the user enters or selects values in the field. Do not use UDO widgets. Determines the appearance and behavior of a field. In character mode, a widget that is not supported is mapped to another widget type. Click a widget to give the field focus. Do not use \"click on\". A field is painted on a component; the widget type is a property of the field. Each widget type has properties of its own. A field has a value; a widget does not. A physical widget can be \"standard\" or \"custom\". A physical widget can be mapped to one or more logical widgets in the initialization file. (The logical widget name appears in the Widget Type list on the Define Field form.) Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}